		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//takingnote.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/08/07/the-hole-in-the-middle-of-the-jobs-report/" data-title="The Hole in the Middle of the Jobs Report" data-description="Job growth without pay raises is a discouraging sign of slack in the job market. ">
